                            <span>16-bit 中间管线</span>
                            <span>基础调色</span>
                            <span>曲线与 HSL</span>
                            <span>参考图风格匹配</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="wm-grade-layout">
                    <div class="wm-before-after" aria-label="调色前后对比">
                        <figure>
                            <img class="wm-grade-before" src="images/home/color-grade-base.jpg" alt="调色前的高山花海" />
                            <figcaption>调色前</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <figure>
                            <img class="wm-grade-after" src="images/home/color-grade-base.jpg" alt="调色后的高山花海" />
                            <figcaption>调色后</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <figure class="wm-workspace-frame wm-workspace-grade">
                        <div class="wm-workspace-composite">
                            <img class="wm-workspace-ui" src="images/home/color-studio.jpg" alt="轻影 16-bit 调色工作台" />
                            <div class="wm-workspace-canvas wm-workspace-canvas-landscape">
                                <img src="images/home/color-grade-base.jpg" alt="调色工作台中正在处理的高山照片" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <figcaption>基础调色、曲线、HSL 与参考图匹配，共用高精度渲染管线。</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="wm-chapter wm-chapter-night">
            <div class="wm-shell">
                <div class="wm-chapter-heading wm-chapter-heading-night">
                    <span class="wm-chapter-number">04</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="wm-kicker">MULTI-FRAME STACK</p>
                        <h2>让时间参与成像</h2>
                        <div class="wm-tags wm-tags-night" aria-label="多帧合成能力">
